reviewText: He was my sensei in 1963 and 1964.  He was great!!
It's a little hard to see the hands at some points it was copied from a video tape so quality is low, other than that it's invaluable

Of all the DVD's in this series that I have purchased and reviewed, This is by far, THE BEST! There is some older film of Shinjo sensei performing all of the Goju kata. There is also older film of him doing weight training. This can be seen on YouTube, but not in the good condition that it is presented here.
